WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:02.710
Good evening, family. Thank you for

00:00:02.720 --> 00:00:05.749
joining me again tonight. Well, we got

00:00:05.759 --> 00:00:08.870
them. I believe the prayers of the

00:00:08.880 --> 00:00:11.190
people from this channel—and you know,

00:00:11.200 --> 00:00:12.629
I know there's a lot of other people

00:00:12.639 --> 00:00:16.470
praying, but we had thousands of

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:18.870
people praying last night at about

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:22.230
the same time that he was turned in. And

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:25.109
so, I think it was within the hour. So,

00:00:25.119 --> 00:00:27.990
I just want to give God some praise that

00:00:28.000 --> 00:00:31.750
prayer works. You know, it's amazing

00:00:31.760 --> 00:00:34.389
when we all come together; many hands

00:00:34.399 --> 00:00:36.790
make light work. And I'm just

00:00:36.800 --> 00:00:39.670
thankful for her

00:00:39.680 --> 00:00:41.590
healing, the wife's healing. What

00:00:41.590 --> 00:00:41.600
is

00:00:41.600 --> 00:00:43.990
it, Erica? Is that right? Erica's

00:00:44.000 --> 00:00:47.510
healing. It helps, you know, to catch

00:00:47.520 --> 00:00:51.430
the person who

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:55.189
murdered her husband. Praise God

00:00:55.199 --> 00:00:57.750
that we found him, that there were no

00:00:57.760 --> 00:01:00.950
other lives lost in this, that the

00:01:00.960 --> 00:01:04.070
law enforcement did a good job,

00:01:04.070 --> 00:01:04.080
and

00:01:04.080 --> 00:01:07.350
that the father had courage enough to

00:01:07.360 --> 00:01:09.109
turn his son in. You know, I

00:01:09.119 --> 00:01:10.230
thought it was interesting that his

00:01:10.240 --> 00:01:11.910
heart was convicted enough that he went

00:01:11.920 --> 00:01:15.910
to his pastor and asked for help and

00:01:15.920 --> 00:01:18.710
counsel. And the pastor said, "Of

00:01:18.720 --> 00:01:21.109
course, you should turn your son

00:01:21.109 --> 00:01:21.119
in,"and

00:01:21.119 --> 00:01:23.030
he held him in his room until the

00:01:23.040 --> 00:01:24.789
authorities got there because his son

00:01:24.799 --> 00:01:27.429
was trying to flee.

00:01:27.439 --> 00:01:29.749
But I believe because of the prayers of

00:01:29.759 --> 00:01:31.830
the righteous, because of us

00:01:31.840 --> 00:01:34.710
praying in agreement that this would be

00:01:34.720 --> 00:01:37.270
quickly resolved, I believe prayer

00:01:37.280 --> 00:01:40.469
changes things. And what an honor to

00:01:40.479 --> 00:01:42.710
be a part of this. I'm so thankful that

00:01:42.720 --> 00:01:44.550
you join me and you take prayer

00:01:44.560 --> 00:01:47.109
seriously in these last of the last

00:01:47.119 --> 00:01:48.870
days.

00:01:50.720 --> 00:01:54.230
I didn't realize that today the UN was

00:01:54.240 --> 00:01:57.590
going to have their vote.

00:01:57.600 --> 00:02:00.069
So, they had their vote today, and

00:02:00.079 --> 00:02:02.310
I guess it was ahead of schedule.

00:02:02.320 --> 00:02:04.950
I was praying that it was

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:07.670
going to happen during the

00:02:07.680 --> 00:02:10.550
week of the 20th—the 22nd, 23rd—that week, but they

00:02:10.560 --> 00:02:14.550
held it the day after 9/11 in the UN.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:17.190
Yesterday, I

00:02:17.200 --> 00:02:20.309
felt it so strong to pray for New York,

00:02:20.319 --> 00:02:24.150
to pray for the two-state solution

00:02:24.160 --> 00:02:26.949
and the things that would be voted upon.

00:02:26.959 --> 00:02:31.350
And there were 10 countries that

00:02:31.350 --> 00:02:31.360
refrained—that

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:34.070
sided with

00:02:34.070 --> 00:02:34.080
Israel—and

00:02:34.080 --> 00:02:35.990
the rest of the world basically

00:02:36.000 --> 00:02:39.030
