00:02:47.920 --> 00:02:49.750
solution.

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:53.589
So France, Saudi Arabia, and

00:02:53.599 --> 00:02:57.030
these other nations are going to try

00:02:57.040 --> 00:03:01.509
to bring more of a framework

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:06.630
in the week of the 20th, 21st,

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:10.309
22nd, 23rd—that week. So, there's more

00:03:10.319 --> 00:03:13.670
prayer to be done, but the vote was

00:03:13.680 --> 00:03:16.630
