00:03:16.640 --> 00:03:20.470
nations are divided: the ones that

00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:22.710
are for Israel and the ones that are not.

00:03:22.720 --> 00:03:25.509
And it's pretty alarming. I

00:03:25.519 --> 00:03:28.149
guess it was 10 countries, and

00:03:28.149 --> 00:03:28.159
they

00:03:28.159 --> 00:03:30.550
were really countries that

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:32.470
didn't have a lot of influence that

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:36.390
stood by Israel. From

00:03:36.400 --> 00:03:39.589
what I understand, even Australia

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:44.070
voted for a two-state solution,

00:03:44.080 --> 00:03:47.910
and Canada, and England. There were so

00:03:47.920 --> 00:03:50.710
