00:03:58.789 --> 00:03:58.799
coming—a

00:03:58.799 --> 00:04:02.710
line that would be

00:04:02.720 --> 00:04:05.830
drawn in the sand of who is for and who

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.589
is against.

00:04:07.599 --> 00:04:10.229
This is an acceleration of what the Lord

00:04:10.239 --> 00:04:12.789
said: a September to remember. And boy,

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:14.949
