00:04:14.959 --> 00:04:17.110
Lord said. I don't think I'll ever

00:04:17.120 --> 00:04:20.469
forget this September, ever,

00:04:20.479 --> 00:04:23.270
already for what we've seen just

00:04:23.280 --> 00:04:27.030
in the first 12 or 13 days.

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:32.550
Incredible, actually—I mean, for how fast

00:04:32.560 --> 00:04:34.790
everything has accelerated,

00:04:34.800 --> 00:04:38.790
even just in this month. But we see

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:42.390
the vote. Thank God the United States of

00:04:42.400 --> 00:04:45.110
