00:13:42.399 --> 00:13:44.870
But it will take us having a backbone

00:13:44.880 --> 00:13:47.430
like a crowbar to stand in the gap and

00:13:47.440 --> 00:13:50.470
say, "Thus far, Satan, and no

00:13:50.470 --> 00:13:50.480
further."Do

00:13:50.480 --> 00:13:52.710
you

00:13:52.710 --> 00:13:52.720
understand?'So,

00:13:52.720 --> 00:13:56.150
as I saw these events taking place

00:13:56.150 --> 00:13:56.160
on

00:13:56.160 --> 00:13:59.509
college campuses, at tailgate parties

00:13:59.519 --> 00:14:02.870
with major events, a man in a green

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:06.550
uniform in Denver, and I've seen

00:14:06.560 --> 00:14:13.269
strategic locations on the Vegas Strip

00:14:13.279 --> 00:14:16.389
where the big pyramid is, where the

00:14:16.399 --> 00:14:20.389
water fountains go off,

00:14:20.389 --> 00:14:20.399
and

00:14:20.399 --> 00:14:23.110
more events.

00:14:23.120 --> 00:14:26.230
The Lord warned me to pray over

00:14:26.240 --> 00:14:29.990
three men.

00:14:30.000 --> 00:14:32.629
It's not just one;

00:14:32.629 --> 00:14:32.639
it's

00:14:32.639 --> 00:14:34.550
three.

00:14:34.560 --> 00:14:40.230
I saw three men strategically marked.

00:14:42.079 --> 00:14:45.350
One is Don Jr., and that's why I told

00:14:45.360 --> 00:14:49.110
you you must pray for this man.

00:14:49.120 --> 00:14:51.829
It's very serious

00:14:51.839 --> 00:14:53.910
to pray a hedge around and about him. It

00:14:53.910 --> 00:14:53.920
was

00:14:53.920 --> 00:14:56.150
nighttime when I saw this

00:14:56.160 --> 00:14:57.829
happen. Now, if it happens in the

00:14:57.839 --> 00:14:59.509
daytime, I don't want to

00:14:59.519 --> 00:15:01.110
help the enemy out. I'm just telling you

00:15:01.110 --> 00:15:01.120
that

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:03.509
I know beyond a shadow of

00:15:03.509 --> 00:15:03.519
a

00:15:03.519 --> 00:15:05.430
doubt what the Lord has told me to pray

00:15:05.440 --> 00:15:08.470
and intercede for this man. He said,

00:15:08.480 --> 00:15:11.990
'Pray for

00:15:11.990 --> 00:15:12.000
him.'He

00:15:12.000 --> 00:15:13.509
tells me these things and He visits

00:15:13.519 --> 00:15:15.750
me, and I feel His presence so strong. He

00:15:15.760 --> 00:15:18.230
says, 'Pray for this man. Pray for

00:15:18.240 --> 00:15:20.470
leaders in the church. Pray for this

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:23.110
because the enemy has a plan to kill,

00:15:23.120 --> 00:15:25.910
steal, and destroy.

00:15:25.920 --> 00:15:29.110
Pray for Donald Trump's health.

00:15:29.120 --> 00:15:32.150
Pray for him, for his heart, and for his

00:15:32.160 --> 00:15:33.910
veins.'I

00:15:33.920 --> 00:15:36.629
saw this, ladies and gentlemen,

00:15:36.639 --> 00:15:38.550
before it came out in the news

00:15:38.560 --> 00:15:43.590
that they were checking all this stuff.

00:15:43.600 --> 00:15:45.990
You can't get that by the flesh; you get

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:47.829
that by the Spirit of God. And I'm not

00:15:47.839 --> 00:15:49.910
listening to a devil; I'm listening to

00:15:49.920 --> 00:15:52.629
the Holy Spirit. I have communion, I

00:15:52.639 --> 00:15:54.949
pray, and I seek His face. And as you

00:15:54.959 --> 00:15:57.269
seek Him, you will find Him. If you

00:15:57.279 --> 00:15:59.910
knock, the door will be opened unto you.

00:15:59.920 --> 00:16:02.310
He said, 'I will do nothing

00:16:02.310 --> 00:16:02.320
on

00:16:02.320 --> 00:16:04.550
this earth without revealing it to my

00:16:04.560 --> 00:16:06.710
prophetic voices first.'Now, I do not

00:16:06.720 --> 00:16:09.430
consider myself a prophet; I consider

00:16:09.440 --> 00:16:11.590
myself a watchman,

00:16:11.600 --> 00:16:14.470
somebody who is called to pray. Now, I

00:16:14.480 --> 00:16:16.069
know there's other prophetic ministries

00:16:16.079 --> 00:16:19.030
on YouTube, and I bless them, but

00:16:19.040 --> 00:16:21.030
I'm just telling you, Brandon Biggs, I

00:16:21.040 --> 00:16:23.509
feel that my wife—the Lord's even told

00:16:23.519 --> 00:16:25.590
us to call our ministry Prayer

00:16:25.600 --> 00:16:26.949
Changes Things. And I couldn't call it

00:16:26.959 --> 00:16:28.389
'Prayer Changes Things

00:16:28.389 --> 00:16:28.399
Church'because

00:16:28.399 --> 00:16:29.749
there was already one there, so I said

00:16:29.759 --> 00:16:32.389
'Foundation.'So,

00:16:32.399 --> 00:16:35.350
I said, 'Prayer Changes

00:16:35.350 --> 00:16:35.360
Things.'That's

00:16:35.360 --> 00:16:37.110
what we're about. That's what

00:16:37.120 --> 00:16:38.790
this YouTube channel, He said, to raise

00:16:38.800 --> 00:16:40.310
up. That's what He said: 'Your main

00:16:40.320 --> 00:16:43.269
mission right now is to raise up

00:16:43.269 --> 00:16:43.279
one

00:16:43.279 --> 00:16:45.430
million people,

00:16:45.430 --> 00:16:45.440
one

00:16:45.440 --> 00:16:48.230
million prayer warriors. And

00:16:48.240 --> 00:16:50.870
through this, I will bring change

00:16:50.880 --> 00:16:53.030
through the channel in prayer across the

00:16:53.040 --> 00:16:56.150
world,

00:16:56.160 --> 00:16:57.990
and the things that I show you will prove to be

00:16:57.990 --> 00:16:58.000
accurate.'Now,

00:16:58.000 --> 00:17:00.629
I'm not

00:17:00.639 --> 00:17:02.550
saying I've always gotten everything

00:17:02.560 --> 00:17:07.429
right; I am human.

00:17:07.439 --> 00:17:10.230
And this is not here to glorify Brandon, I

00:17:10.240 --> 00:17:12.710
can assure you of that.

00:17:12.720 --> 00:17:14.390
Nobody's going to go, 'Well, Brandon, he is

00:17:14.390 --> 00:17:14.400
awesome.'It's

00:17:14.400 --> 00:17:17.270
never

00:17:17.280 --> 00:17:19.909
to glorify man.

00:17:19.919 --> 00:17:22.150
So maybe He lets you

00:17:22.160 --> 00:17:25.270
miss it, because

00:17:25.280 --> 00:17:26.949
it keeps you humble. It keeps you all

00:17:26.959 --> 00:17:28.390
cleaned up so you don't get a big head

00:17:28.400 --> 00:17:30.150
and go, 'Well, I'm such-a-much.'No, I

00:17:30.160 --> 00:17:33.190
am not such-a-much. I'm just Brandon,

00:17:33.200 --> 00:17:35.270
and I pray just like you do, and I put

00:17:35.280 --> 00:17:37.270
my clothes on just like you do, and I've

00:17:37.280 --> 00:17:38.870
got stuff I'm working through just like

00:17:38.880 --> 00:17:41.750
you do. Every single one of us has

00:17:41.760 --> 00:17:43.990
something we're working through. And

00:17:44.000 --> 00:17:45.750
anytime you think you're bigger and

00:17:45.750 --> 00:17:45.760
better—like

00:17:45.760 --> 00:17:47.190
I've seen a lot of other

00:17:47.200 --> 00:17:49.190
ministers, they try to have a big head

00:17:49.200 --> 00:17:50.549
and walk through, and you

00:17:50.559 --> 00:17:51.909
can't even get them through the doorway

00:17:51.919 --> 00:17:53.909
because their head is so big. And I've

00:17:53.919 --> 00:17:56.630
been raised around them; I see

00:17:56.640 --> 00:17:58.310
them, and they don't have time

00:17:58.320 --> 00:18:00.870
for you. They have big heads. But I'm

00:18:00.880 --> 00:18:02.230
going to tell you this: it's time to

00:18:02.240 --> 00:18:05.270
deflate some egos up in here and realize

00:18:05.280 --> 00:18:07.430
that we're all human, we're all saved

00:18:07.440 --> 00:18:10.070
by grace, and all of us have a call to do

00:18:10.080 --> 00:18:12.549
something to reach the lost. Every

00:18:12.559 --> 00:18:14.390
single one of us—not one of us

00:18:14.390 --> 00:18:14.400
is

00:18:14.400 --> 00:18:16.630
better than the other. God's called

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:18.310
every single one of you to do something

00:18:18.320 --> 00:18:21.270
big for Him. I was a janitor for

00:18:21.270 --> 00:18:21.280
fifteen

00:18:21.280 --> 00:18:23.270
years, and I was looked down upon for

00:18:23.280 --> 00:18:26.390
a lot of my life, with

00:18:26.400 --> 00:18:28.150
learning disabilities all through

00:18:28.160 --> 00:18:30.470
school and all the things that I've been

00:18:30.480 --> 00:18:32.470
through. But I can tell you, I've been at

00:18:32.480 --> 00:18:34.230
the bottom of the barrel where everybody

00:18:34.240 --> 00:18:36.710
looks at you as nothing, and then I've

00:18:36.720 --> 00:18:38.070
been at the top, and they still look at

00:18:38.080 --> 00:18:40.470
you similarly. But I'm going to tell you

00:18:40.480 --> 00:18:42.390
this: it's not about how man looks at

00:18:42.400 --> 00:18:44.390
you; it's about how Jesus looks at you

00:18:44.400 --> 00:18:46.549
and how much He has a hand on you. And

00:18:46.559 --> 00:18:48.789
you do exactly what He's told you to do,

00:18:48.799 --> 00:18:52.070
and you'll do it with great victory.

00:18:52.080 --> 00:18:54.870
I need you to be real.

00:18:54.880 --> 00:18:57.510
All this Hollywood celebrity

00:18:57.520 --> 00:18:59.990
crap is over. Do you understand?

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:03.830
Hollywood Christianity is over.

00:19:03.840 --> 00:19:07.110
It's all hands on deck, all striving for

00:19:07.120 --> 00:19:09.909
the call to say, 'Jesus,

00:19:09.919 --> 00:19:12.870
I'm here. Use me.'You could be the

00:19:12.880 --> 00:19:15.430
gardener or you could be worth billions,

00:19:15.440 --> 00:19:17.510
but either way, you're going to stand

00:19:17.520 --> 00:19:19.190
before the Father, and He's going to

00:19:19.200 --> 00:19:21.029
judge your works. He's going to say,

00:19:21.039 --> 00:19:24.150
'You know what? You had a big ego

00:19:24.160 --> 00:19:26.390
and all these things, and all you

00:19:26.400 --> 00:19:28.710
did was for the praise of

00:19:28.710 --> 00:19:28.720
men.'Whatever

00:19:28.720 --> 00:19:30.870
you do, in word

00:19:30.870 --> 00:19:30.880
or

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:33.510
deed, do it all to the glory of God.

00:19:33.520 --> 00:19:35.669
I don't need somebody to tell me, 'Well

00:19:35.679 --> 00:19:37.190
done, Brandon,'because I'm looking for

00:19:37.200 --> 00:19:40.230
a 'Well done'from Him. And when I get up

00:19:40.240 --> 00:19:42.470
there, I want Him to say, 'Look,

00:19:42.480 --> 00:19:44.870
Brandon, you get to do all this in

00:19:44.870 --> 00:19:44.880
the

00:19:44.880 --> 00:19:46.630
thousand years because you kept your

00:19:46.640 --> 00:19:48.950
heart right before Me and you humbled

00:19:48.960 --> 00:19:51.510
yourself before Me all the time. You

00:19:51.520 --> 00:19:54.950
never let ego get in

00:19:54.950 --> 00:19:54.960
the way.'That's

00:19:54.960 --> 00:19:57.510
why I'm continually looking for ways

00:19:57.520 --> 00:19:59.990
that I can sow in private so I can reap

00:20:00.000 --> 00:20:02.549
openly over in the thousand years. You

00:20:02.559 --> 00:20:06.390
don't understand—I've seen it.

00:20:06.400 --> 00:20:08.710
We have a lifetime

00:20:08.710 --> 00:20:08.720
where

00:20:08.720 --> 00:20:11.909
usually, if

00:20:11.919 --> 00:20:13.990
you're blessed, you live past

00:20:14.000 --> 00:20:15.909
80.

00:20:15.919 --> 00:20:18.070
So we

00:20:18.070 --> 00:20:18.080
have

00:20:18.080 --> 00:20:20.470
this ten

00:20:20.470 --> 00:20:20.480
percent

00:20:20.480 --> 00:20:22.710
to

00:20:22.710 --> 00:20:22.720
sow...

00:20:22.720 --> 00:20:27.590
this ten percent is maybe less to

00:20:27.590 --> 00:20:27.600
sow

00:20:27.600 --> 00:20:32.789
into the thousand years to reap that,

00:20:32.799 --> 00:20:35.830
but I want to sow into the thousand

00:20:35.840 --> 00:20:39.350
years. What I am doing on this side

00:20:39.360 --> 00:20:41.029
of the earth right now

00:20:41.029 --> 00:20:41.039
is

00:20:41.039 --> 00:20:43.110
so that I reap a great harvest for the

00:20:43.110 --> 00:20:43.120
thousand-year

00:20:43.120 --> 00:20:45.350
reign.

00:20:45.360 --> 00:20:47.590
And yeah, you may say,

00:20:47.590 --> 00:20:47.600
'Well...'but

00:20:47.600 --> 00:20:49.270
I'm telling

00:20:49.280 --> 00:20:51.110
you all, that's what Brandon's

00:20:51.120 --> 00:20:53.029
doing, that's what Diana's doing, and that's

00:20:53.039 --> 00:20:55.110
what we're doing when we say, 'You know

00:20:55.110 --> 00:20:55.120
what?'We

00:20:55.120 --> 00:20:58.310
may not be

00:20:58.320 --> 00:21:00.630
around the king's table on this earth or

00:21:00.640 --> 00:21:02.710
whatever, but I'm around the king's

00:21:02.720 --> 00:21:05.430
table in heaven."Do you understand?

00:21:05.440 --> 00:21:08.789
That's what it's about to me. I want so

00:21:08.799 --> 00:21:12.070
bad for Him to say, "Well done, thy good

00:21:12.080 --> 00:21:13.909
and faithful servant,"just like I

00:21:13.919 --> 00:21:17.029
believe He did with Charlie.

00:21:17.039 --> 00:21:18.950
"Well done, thy good and faithful

00:21:18.960 --> 00:21:21.350
servant. You did it.

00:21:21.360 --> 00:21:25.190
You did it. Enter into My

00:21:25.190 --> 00:21:25.200
rest."And

00:21:25.200 --> 00:21:28.470
so, I want to encourage you all

00:21:28.480 --> 00:21:30.789
to

00:21:30.799 --> 00:21:34.549
deflate all ego,

00:21:34.559 --> 00:21:37.510
to deflate it, and just be real. When you

00:21:37.520 --> 00:21:39.270
get real with God, He will get real

00:21:39.280 --> 00:21:41.110
with you.

00:21:41.120 --> 00:21:43.830
He'll become real to you.

00:21:43.840 --> 00:21:45.669
When you get real with God, He'll become

00:21:45.679 --> 00:21:47.190
real to you. That's a better way to say

00:21:47.200 --> 00:21:49.110
it.

00:21:49.120 --> 00:21:51.110
He'll become real to your inner man,

00:21:51.120 --> 00:21:53.510
because you're not trying to be

00:21:53.520 --> 00:21:55.510
something that you're not. He sees right

00:21:55.520 --> 00:21:57.590
through it.

00:21:57.600 --> 00:21:59.830
He sees right through it. You are not

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:02.070
pretending. You're not covering

00:22:02.080 --> 00:22:04.710
things up, and He sees through every

00:22:04.720 --> 00:22:07.270
motive of why you do it when you do it,

00:22:07.280 --> 00:22:10.070
and your heart motive of the deepest

00:22:10.080 --> 00:22:12.149
thing that you think you're covering up.

00:22:12.159 --> 00:22:14.070
Maybe even your wife or your husband

00:22:14.070 --> 00:22:14.080
doesn't

00:22:14.080 --> 00:22:16.470
see it, but the Father sees it

00:22:16.480 --> 00:22:20.390
all, and you're not fooling nobody.

00:22:20.400 --> 00:22:22.950
You're not fooling Him.

00:22:22.960 --> 00:22:26.549
The motives of the heart. And that's why

00:22:26.559 --> 00:22:28.230
I say, that's why I believe David says,

00:22:28.240 --> 00:22:31.029
"Search me and know me. Create in me a

00:22:31.039 --> 00:22:33.750
clean heart,

00:22:33.750 --> 00:22:33.760
O

00:22:33.760 --> 00:22:40.230
God."I

00:22:40.240 --> 00:22:43.270
want you to really search

00:22:43.280 --> 00:22:45.029
yourself. That's why I do it all

00:22:45.039 --> 00:22:47.909
the time. I do it. I do it continually.

00:22:47.919 --> 00:22:50.310
"God, show me,

00:22:50.320 --> 00:22:53.350
create in me a clean heart. Purify me.

00:22:53.360 --> 00:22:56.310
Purify my heart, Lord, through the

00:22:56.320 --> 00:22:59.029
refining refiner's fire, that You

00:22:59.039 --> 00:23:01.110
burn out the chaff. Burn out the

00:23:01.120 --> 00:23:04.230
trash in my life, and expose

00:23:04.240 --> 00:23:06.230
the darkness, the hidden things that

00:23:06.240 --> 00:23:09.350
maybe I don't even realize.

00:23:09.360 --> 00:23:12.710
Expose it and clean me. Make me new

00:23:12.720 --> 00:23:15.190
before You, Father,

00:23:15.200 --> 00:23:18.630
so that You're able to use this vessel.

00:23:18.640 --> 00:23:20.549
I don't want nothing hindering me at

00:23:20.559 --> 00:23:24.710
all."People

00:23:24.720 --> 00:23:26.549
are very concerned: "Brandon, you

00:23:26.559 --> 00:23:27.990
say a lot of things. Are you not worried

00:23:28.000 --> 00:23:29.669
to be like a Charlie?"I'm going to tell

00:23:29.679 --> 00:23:33.430
you this: I don't think that way.

00:23:33.440 --> 00:23:35.990
I don't think that way.

00:23:36.000 --> 00:23:38.390
You can't let fear in like that and let

00:23:38.390 --> 00:23:38.400
it

00:23:38.400 --> 00:23:39.990
bombard your thoughts. You know why? I

00:23:40.000 --> 00:23:41.590
cast down every high imagination that

00:23:41.600 --> 00:23:44.230
exalts itself above the word of God. I

00:23:44.240 --> 00:23:46.950
put my thoughts on the word.

00:23:46.960 --> 00:23:48.870
Yeah, I understand I say a lot of

00:23:48.880 --> 00:23:50.630
controversial things, but I know that

00:23:50.640 --> 00:23:52.310
greater is He that is in me than he that

00:23:52.320 --> 00:23:53.830
is in the world. And I believe that a

00:23:53.840 --> 00:23:55.830
thousand shall fall at my side and ten thousand

00:23:55.830 --> 00:23:55.840
at my right

00:23:55.840 --> 00:23:58.230
hand. And if it comes down

00:23:58.240 --> 00:24:00.630
to it and you go home, you go home with

00:24:00.640 --> 00:24:02.950
your head held high,

00:24:02.960 --> 00:24:05.750
saying, "I did exactly what my

00:24:05.760 --> 00:24:11.990
Father has told me to

00:24:11.990 --> 00:24:12.000
do."The

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:15.190
Lord specifically said to me, "Are

00:24:15.200 --> 00:24:19.909
you willing to die for Me?

00:24:19.919 --> 00:24:22.870
Are you willing to die for the cause of

00:24:22.870 --> 00:24:22.880
Me?"He

00:24:22.880 --> 00:24:26.870
stood in my living room. It was

00:24:26.880 --> 00:24:30.390
not an open-eye vision.

00:24:30.400 --> 00:24:32.950
You may not believe it, but He did. I

00:24:32.960 --> 00:24:34.950
can tell you what He was wearing. I can

00:24:34.960 --> 00:24:37.190
tell you what He had on. He turned back

00:24:37.200 --> 00:24:38.789
around and He looked at me very gruff,

00:24:38.799 --> 00:24:40.390
and He put His finger right in my face

00:24:40.400 --> 00:24:42.950
and He said, "Are you willing to die for

00:24:42.960 --> 00:24:50.470
the cause of Christ, for

00:24:50.470 --> 00:24:50.480
Me?"I

00:24:50.480 --> 00:24:53.830
shook

00:24:53.840 --> 00:24:55.510
because I knew there was no way I could

00:24:55.520 --> 00:24:57.269
hide from it. He could see everything

00:24:57.279 --> 00:24:59.350
about me at that moment, and there's no

00:24:59.360 --> 00:25:01.750
way you can lie.

00:25:01.760 --> 00:25:05.510
And so, "Oh yes,

00:25:05.510 --> 00:25:05.520
Lord."He

00:25:05.520 --> 00:25:07.669
can see it.

00:25:07.679 --> 00:25:10.710
